\
<p>A classic take out favourite made at home! And we promise, it\'92s actually better than take out. Pair with our Free Run IPA to complete a delicious dinner.</p>\
\
/* Lightbox text */\
\
<p><span class=\'93recipe-highlight\'94>Enjoy this homemade chicken fried rice with a Free Run IPA!<span> Who would have thought you could make chicken fried rice at home that tastes better than take out! We did! And we blame it all on the delicious <span class=\'93egg\'94>scrambled egg</span>. You can swap the chicken out with just about any protein you\'92d like- pork, shrimp, even tofu. The best part? It\'92s cooked in ONE pan and it only takes a half hour</p>\
